Read Data

library(tidyverse)
library(hrbrthemes)
podes <- read_csv("Podes 2018\\Explorasi\\podes2018_desa_part2.csv")
desa <- podes %>%
  group_by(R101N) %>%
  summarise(n = n())

klb <- podes %>% filter(KLB == 1) %>%
  group_by(R101N) %>%
  summarise(total_klb = sum(KLB))

desa %>% left_join(klb) %>%
  mutate(percent_klb = total_klb/n)

Kejadian Luar Biasa (KLB) Berdasarkan Jenis dan Provinsi

  to0 <- function(x)(x == 1)
  podes %>%
    select(R101N, starts_with("R709")) %>%
    select(R101N, ends_with("K2")) %>%
    mutate_if(is.numeric, to0) %>%
    group_by(R101N) %>%
    summarise_all(list(sum)) %>%
    rename(Provinsi = R101N, Muntaber = R709AK2, DBD = R709BK2, Campak = R709CK2,  Malaria = R709DK2,  SARS = R709EK2, Hepatitis = R709FK2, Difteri = R709GK2, Lainnya = R709HK2) %>%
    pivot_longer(Muntaber:Lainnya, names_to = "jenis_klb", values_to = "jumlah_desa") %>%
    
    ggplot(aes(x=jenis_klb, y=jumlah_desa, fill=Provinsi)) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge())+
    scale_fill_brewer(palette="Paired")+
    theme_ipsum() +

    ggtitle("Kejadian Luar Biasa (KLB) Berdasarkan Jenis dan Provinsi") +
    xlab("Jenis KLB") + 
    ylab("Jumlah Desa Desa")

Keberadaan Faskes

Jumlah Faskes vs KLB

podes %>%
  mutate(faskes = R704AK2 +  R704CK2 + R704DK2 + R704EK2 + R704FK2 + R704GK2 ) %>%
  filter(faskes > 0) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=as.factor(KLB), y=faskes)) +

  labs(title="Sebaran Jumlah Fasilitas Kesehatan",

podes %>%
  mutate(faskes = R704AK2 +  R704CK2 + R704DK2 + R704EK2 + R704FK2 + R704GK2, klb = as.factor(KLB) ) %>%
  filter(faskes > 0) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=faskes, group = klb, fill = klb)) +
  geom_density(adjust=1.5, alpha=.4) +
  theme_ipsum() +
  labs(title="Sebaran Jumlah Fasilitas Kesehatan",

RS

  podes %>%
    mutate(faskes = R704AK2 > 0) %>%
    group_by(faskes, KLB) %>%
    summarise(n = n()) %>%
    group_by(faskes) %>%
    mutate(prop = n/sum(n)) %>%
    
    ggplot(aes(fill=as.factor(KLB), y=prop, x=faskes)) + 
    geom_bar(position="fill", stat="identity") +
    scale_fill_discrete(name = "KLB", labels=c('Ada KLB', 'Tidak Ada')) +
    theme_ipsum() +
    labs(title="Rumah Sakit",
         x="Keberadaan Rumah Sakit", y = "Proporsi Desa")

Fatality Rate

  rs <- podes %>%
    mutate(faskes=R704AK2 > 0) %>%
    filter(KLB == 1) %>%
    group_by(faskes) %>%
    summarise(fatality = sum(KLB_MENINGGAL)/sum(KLB_PENDERITA )) %>%
    mutate(name = "Rumah Sakit")
  
  puskesmas <- podes %>%
    mutate(faskes= R704CK2 + R704DK2 + R704EK2 > 0) %>%
    filter(KLB == 1) %>%
    group_by(faskes) %>%
    summarise(fatality = sum(KLB_MENINGGAL)/sum(KLB_PENDERITA )) %>%
    mutate(name = "Puskesmas")
  
  poliklinik <- podes %>%
    mutate(faskes= R704CK2 + R704DK2 + R704EK2 > 0) %>%
    filter(KLB == 1) %>%
    group_by(faskes) %>%
    summarise(fatality = sum(KLB_MENINGGAL)/sum(KLB_PENDERITA )) %>%
    mutate(name = "Poliklinik")
  
 dokter <- podes %>%
    mutate(faskes=R704GK2 > 0) %>%
    filter(KLB == 1) %>%
    group_by(faskes) %>%
    summarise(fatality = sum(KLB_MENINGGAL)/sum(KLB_PENDERITA )) %>%
    mutate(name = "Praktik Dokter")
rbind(rs, puskesmas, poliklinik, dokter) %>%
  mutate(Keberadaan = faskes, Faskes = as.factor(name)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(fill=Keberadaan, y=fatality, x=Faskes)) + 
  geom_bar(position="dodge", stat="identity") +
  theme_ipsum() +
  labs(title="Fatality Rate Berdasarkan Faskes")

Additional Data from INDO-DAPOER

indodapoer <- read_csv("Podes 2018\\Explorasi\\indo-dapoer-add.csv", na = "..")
indodapoer_tidy <- 
  indodapoer %>% 
    pivot_longer(
      cols = starts_with("20"),
      names_to = "year",
      values_to = "value",
      values_drop_na = TRUE
    ) %>%
    rename(province = `Provinces Name`, province.code = `Provinces Code`) %>%
    mutate(province = toupper(sub(',.+', '', province)), year = as.factor(sub(' .+','', year))) %>%
    select(-`Series Name`) %>%
    pivot_wider(names_from = `Series Code`, values_from = value) %>%
    rename_with(tolower)
# join podes-indodapoer
podapoer <- desa %>% left_join(klb) %>%
  mutate(percent_klb = total_klb/n) %>%
  dplyr::rename(province = R101N) %>%
  left_join(indodapoer_tidy)

podapoer2 <- podapoer %>%
  select(-province.code, -year) %>%
  mutate(percent_klb = percent_klb*100) %>%
  pivot_longer(names_to = "variable", values_to = "value", n:sp.pop.totl)
podapoer2 %>%
  filter(variable == 'percent_klb' | variable == 'hou.sta.acsn.zs') %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = province, y = value, fill = variable)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") +
  scale_fill_discrete(name = "Variable", labels=c('% Access To Sanitation','% KLB')) +
  theme_ipsum() +
  labs(title="% KLB vs Access To Sanitation",
         x="Province", y = "Percent") + theme(legend.position = "bottom")

podapoer2 %>%
  filter(variable == 'percent_klb' | variable == 'hou.h2o.acsn.zs') %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = province, y = value, fill = variable)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", position = "dodge") +
  scale_fill_discrete(name = "Variable", labels=c('% Access to Safe Water','% KLB')) +
  theme_ipsum() +
  labs(title="% KLB vs Access to Safe Water",

podapoer2 %>%

Multivariate

Histogram Beberapa Indikator Berdasarkan Keberadaan KLB

podes_kab <- 
  podes %>% 
  mutate(across(matches('R709.K2'), function(i){i == 1})) %>%
  mutate(klb = R709AK2 + R709BK2 + R709CK2 + R709DK2 + R709EK2 + R709FK2 + R709GK2 + R709HK2 > 1) %>%
  group_by(R101N, R102N, klb) %>%
  summarise(ndesa = n(),
            nklb = sum(klb),
            menderita = sum(R709AK3 + R709BK3 + R709CK3 + R709DK3 + R709EK3 + R709FK3 + R709GK3 + R709HK3),
            meninggal = sum(R709AK4 + R709BK4 + R709CK4 + R709DK4 + R709EK4 + R709FK4 + R709GK4 + R709HK4),
            faskes = sum(R704AK2 + R704CK2 + R704DK2 + R704EK2 + R704FK2 + R704GK2 + R704JK2 + R704LK2),
            nakes = sum(R706A1+R706A2+R706B+R706C+R706D)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  rename(prov = R101N, kab = R102N)
h1 <- podes_kab %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = ndesa)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 fill = "cornflowerblue") +
  facet_grid(~ klb) +
  labs(subtitle  = "Jumlah Desa") +
  theme_ipsum()
h2 <- podes_kab %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = menderita)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 fill = "cornflowerblue") +
  facet_grid(~ klb) +
  labs(subtitle  = "Jumlah Penderita") +
  theme_ipsum()
h3 <- podes_kab %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = meninggal)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 fill = "cornflowerblue") +
  facet_grid(~ klb) +
  labs(subtitle  = "Jumlah Meninggal") +
  theme_ipsum()
h4 <- podes_kab %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = faskes)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 fill = "cornflowerblue") +
  facet_grid(~ klb) +
  labs(subtitle  = "Jumlah Faskes") +
  theme_ipsum()
h5 <- podes_kab %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = nakes)) +
  geom_histogram(color = "white",
                 fill = "cornflowerblue") +
  facet_grid(~ klb) +
  labs(subtitle  = "Jumlah Nakes") +
  theme_ipsum()
library(cowplot)
plot_grid(
  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5,
  ncol = 2
)

Additional Data from INDO-DAPOER

indodapoer <- read_csv("Podes 2018\\Explorasi\\indo-dapoer-add2.csv", na = "..")
indodapoer_tidy <- 
  indodapoer %>% 
  filter(!grepl('Prop.$', `Provinces Name`)) %>%
    pivot_longer(
      cols = starts_with("20"),
      names_to = "year",
      values_to = "value",
      values_drop_na = TRUE
    ) %>%
    rename(kab = `Provinces Name`, kab.code = `Provinces Code`) %>%
    mutate(kab = toupper(sub(',.+', '', kab)), year = as.factor(sub(' .+','', year))) %>%
    select(-`Series Name`) %>%
    pivot_wider(names_from = `Series Code`, values_from = value) %>%
    rename(birth_by_nakes = SH.STA.BRTC.ZS, access_to_sanitation = HOU.STA.ACSN.ZS,
           access_to_safe_water = HOU.H2O.ACSN.ZS, poverty_rate = SI.POV.BPL,
           morbidity_rate = SH.MORB.ZS, total_population = SP.POP.TOTL) %>%
  select(kab, birth_by_nakes, access_to_sanitation, access_to_safe_water, morbidity_rate, poverty_rate, total_population)

podes_kab2 <- podes_kab %>%
  group_by(kab) %>%
  summarise(ndesa = sum(ndesa), nklb =sum(nklb)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  mutate(klb_rate = 100*nklb/ndesa) %>%
  left_join(indodapoer_tidy)
ggpairs(podes_kab2,
        columns = 4:10,
        title = 'Correlation Plot dari Beberapa Indikator KLB (Data Indo-dapoer)') + 
  theme_ipsum()
